[<a href="/definition/chaga#jyotisha" title="Goto “Chaga” definition">«previous</a> 
<a itemprop="url" href="/jyotisha/glossary/c" title="Jyotisha glossary starting with c">(C)</a>

<a href="/definition/chardana#jyotisha" title="Goto “Chardana” definition">next»</a>]
— 

Chandas in <a href="/jyotisha" title="Jyotisha glossary homepage"><span itemprop="name">Jyotisha glossary</span></a>
